commitResults.messageTitle: Fix checkstyle and change UI behaviour
commitResults.messageBody:
Previously UI got the profile picture from the model. However
now it gets it directly from the data/profilepictures folder using
path in the profilePic field of Person.

storageManager (uses StorageManager::saveProfilePicture, etc).

abstraction

commitResults.messageBody:
`11.x.xx` seems clearer, compared to the `*.**`, which seems like it
could potentially be some leftover symbols/formatting issues.

PR #128 included JavaFX web in the `build.gradle` file, which increased
our the filesize of the generated JAR file to close to 100MB. Since we
aren't using any of the features there, the dependency, along with
various references in the test files which weren't being utilized can be
removed. This restores the JAR filesize to ~10MB as well.
Thank you vim!
